# Southern USA (Census-style) names in the 1980s: common + distinctive ("unique") in-region
where 
  names.year between 1980 and 1989
  and names.state in ('AL','AR','DE','FL','GA','KY','LA','MD','MS','NC','OK','SC','TN','TX','VA','WV')

select
  names.name,
  names.gender,
  sum(names.births) as south_births_80s,
  sum(names.total_births) as us_births_80s,
  avg(names.percent_of_total) as avg_south_share_of_us,
  rank(names.name) over (partition by names.gender order by sum(names.births) desc) as common_rank_in_south,
  rank(names.name) over (partition by names.gender order by avg(names.percent_of_total) desc) as unique_rank_by_south_share

having
  south_births_80s >= 200

order by
  common_rank_in_south asc,
  unique_rank_by_south_share asc

limit 200;

results.response:
# Star Wars impact on baby names (SSA): baseline vs post-1977 uplift
where names.year between 1960 and 2023
select
    names.name,
    sum(names.births) as births,
    sum(names.births) by names.name, names.year as births_by_year,
    names.year,

    # percent-of-total for this name in a given year (across all states/genders)
    (sum(names.births) by names.name, names.year)
      /
    (sum(names.births) by names.year) as pct_of_births_that_year,

    # baseline (pre-Star Wars) avg share: 1970-1976
    avg(
        (
            (sum(names.births) by names.name, names.year)
              /
            (sum(names.births) by names.year)
        ) ? (names.year between 1970 and 1976)
    ) by names.name as baseline_pct_1970_1976,

    # peak post-1977 share and peak-year share (1977+)
    max(
        (
            (sum(names.births) by names.name, names.year)
              /
            (sum(names.births) by names.year)
        ) ? (names.year >= 1977)
    ) by names.name as peak_post_1977_pct,

    max(names.year ? (names.year >= 1977)) by names.name as latest_year_in_window,

    # peak uplift vs baseline (percentage points)
    (peak_post_1977_pct - baseline_pct_1970_1976) as peak_uplift_pct_points,

    # rank names by uplift
    rank(names.name) over (order by peak_uplift_pct_points desc) as uplift_rank

having
    names.name in ('Luke','Leia','Han','Anakin','Padme','Rey','Kylo','Finn','Poe','Obi','Lando','Chewbacca','Yoda')
    and uplift_rank <= 50
order by
    uplift_rank asc,
    names.year asc
limit 500;

results.response:
where names.year between 1960 and 2023
select
  names.name,

  # baseline (pre-Star Wars) average share of births, 1970-1976
  avg(
    (
      (sum(names.births) by names.name, names.year)
      /
      (sum(names.births) by names.year)
    ) ? (names.year between 1970 and 1976)
  ) by names.name as baseline_share_1970_1976,

  # peak post-1977 share of births and the year it occurs
  max(
    (
      (sum(names.births) by names.name, names.year)
      /
      (sum(names.births) by names.year)
    ) ? (names.year >= 1977)
  ) by names.name as peak_share_post_1977,

  max(
    names.year ?
      (
        (names.year >= 1977)
        and
        (
          (
            (sum(names.births) by names.name, names.year)
            /
            (sum(names.births) by names.year)
          )
          =
          max(
            (
              (sum(names.births) by names.name, names.year)
              /
              (sum(names.births) by names.year)
            ) ? (names.year >= 1977)
          ) by names.name
        )
      )
  ) by names.name as peak_year_post_1977,

  # uplift in percentage points (share units)
  (peak_share_post_1977 - baseline_share_1970_1976) as peak_uplift_share,

  # context: total births for the name (all years in window)
  sum(names.births) by names.name as total_births_1960_2023,

  rank(names.name) over (order by peak_uplift_share desc) as impact_rank

having
  names.name in (
    'Luke','Leia','Han','Anakin','Padme','Rey','Kylo','Finn','Poe',
    'Obi','Lando','Yoda','Chewbacca'
  )
order by
  impact_rank asc
limit 100;

    when game_tall.team.color in (

  avg(game_tall.win) as win_rate

  win_rate desc
